<HL>
   Meredith to Sell Unit
</HL>
<DATE>
04/18/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A16
</SO>
<CO>
   MDP
</CO>
<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
</IN>
<LP>
   DES MOINES, Iowa -- Meredith Corp. said that it agreed in
principle to sell its MMT Sales Inc. unit to a management
group.
   The publishing and broadcasting concern said terms are
being negotiated.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   MMT is a New York-based advertising sales concern that
represents 30 television stations, including Meredith-owned
stations.
</TEXT>
